features: 【Multifunction Dresser】 Use stylish storage organizers to find endless organizational possibilities. Just place this clothing storage in the closet to offer a home for workout gear, blankets; place it in the nursery as a kids dresser to store baby clothes and baby stuff; place it in the entryway for storage saving unit for frequently used items.

【Large Capacity】8 drawers are to satisfy various storage needs. The wood top is great for keeping the most-used items within your reach. With plentiful space to organize all your belongings, your room will always be kept in perfect order.

【Durable Material】This tall dresser is made of cationic materials, all other sides and gaps are made of high-quality breathable and non-woven synthetic fiber, harmless and wear-resistant, suitable for kids, teens and adults. Easy-pull drawers for smooth sliding and closing. For easy cleaning, just wipe with damp cloth and get it air-dried.

【Quality Construction】This fabric dresser combines water-resistant MDF board with a durable steel frame. A triangular stable structure to make it sturdy under load 66lb. Anti-tipping accessories are also equipped to prevent accidents. With 4 adjustable feet, you won’t have to worry about stability, and it is also adaptable to different spaces.

【Easy to Assemble】The packages will come with all the tools and accessories for quick assembly, which allows only about 20 minutes to assemble your storage drawers with detailed instructions and the installation video. If you have encountered any problems, we would be delighted to help you find a solution and reply to your email within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice storage unit
reviews.reviewText: Purchased this unit to use as a dresser. I didn’t want to spend a lot of money & wanted something that I can move easily in case I wanted use in another room other than a bedroom. This unit is great for the price, easy to assemble by one person. Comes with everything needed to assemble including the Phillip screwdriver & Ellen wrench. The quality of the material drawers are thick so they pretty strong with the liner that goes inside for them to keep their box shape. The material is a dark grey for the drawers & the frame is metal and looks very nice once put together.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute little dresser
reviews.reviewText: I'll admit, I was a bit intimidated when I opened the box. But, I was surprised by how easy it was to put together. All the pieces were numbered and lettered and the instructions were super simple to follow. All the hardware and tools needed were included. I read reviews where people had a hard time putting the handles on the drawers. I did not have any issues as long as you put in one screw at a time. Can't attest to durability yet as I just put it together but it seems sturdy and holds everything I need it to. I would definitely buy this again. 😊

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for what we were looking for
reviews.reviewText: Great for an affordable dresser. The cloth drawers are perfect for storing clothes. It was easy to put together. I wish the handles weren’t plastic but so far it has been durable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The product is honestly great, it was cheap, easy to assemble and my husband loves having different drawers to categorize his clothing. however, i am 38 weeks pregnant and we’ve had this for 3 weeks now and i kid you not, these drawers smell. only way i can describe it is stale fart. i’ve been up and down my room cleaning it, trying to figure out why my room smells like a bomb went off every morning only to realize it was the dang drawers. before i put into my room, i sprayed them down with lysol and left them outside to air out for about 6 hours. didn’t work lmao so besides the smell, product is great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good for the price
reviews.reviewText: Nice overall, very sturdy frame, easy to assemble. The drawers are cloth, but have a solid front and bottom so are fairly sturdy. The drawers are somewhat smaller than expected, but work for what I need.
